name: UFO Travel
description:
• It is a very fun and addictive game, it has a combination of different types of games, you will have to go through various obstacles to reach the final boss.
  • It has something similar to the famous game Flappy Bird, in terms of mobility. But it is completely different from that game, I have not seen this style of play before.
  • You just have to go through different levels, dodging obstacles and killing different monsters through the infinity of space.
